1
00:00:19,480 --> 00:00:20,440
Boss Wu, you're here.

2
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:23,640
Open the door!

3
00:00:24,440 --> 00:00:25,879
Is that punk who won my money here?

4
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:26,879
He didn't come.

5
00:00:27,399 --> 00:00:28,399
Your friend's here.

6
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:17,120
This case,

7
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:19,719
after the media coverage,

8
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,680
has caused quite a stir in Fengdu.

9
00:01:21,959 --> 00:01:24,319
Many fabricated versions of the cause of death have surfaced.

10
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:26,000
The city leadership is taking it very seriously.

11
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:28,000
They have ordered us to solve this case as soon as possible.

12
00:01:28,599 --> 00:01:30,599
Kaiyang, you need to step up the pace.

13
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:32,879
Jiang Han, share your thoughts.

14
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:35,280
Economic Crimes has been investigating

15
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:36,920
Chengming Machinery's massive loan fraud case.

16
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,879
And the main player in that fraud is Shen Qing.

17
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:41,079
How did Shen Qing bypass Director Su Zhuang

18
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,400
to obtain the loan paperwork?

19
00:01:42,799 --> 00:01:44,200
There are many suspicious points here.

20
00:01:45,079 --> 00:01:46,840
Chief Xing, speaking of Su Zhuang,

21
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,959
I suggest we list him as a key suspect.

22
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:49,840
Hmm.

23
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:52,599
Su Zhuang's influence in Fengdu cannot be underestimated.

24
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:55,519
We cannot afford any mistakes investigating him.

25
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:59,280
Chief Xing, the answer to any homicide case

26
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:01,200
is uncovered by resolving discrepancies along the way.

27
00:02:04,079 --> 00:02:05,920
I agree, but let me reiterate:

28
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:06,959
No matter who it is,

29
00:02:07,079 --> 00:02:08,039
if they break the law,

30
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:08,960
we will show no leniency.

31
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:09,919
Yes, sir.

32
00:02:15,159 --> 00:02:17,879
The fatal fall of Fengdu Bank's credit director

33
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:20,159
has shaken the city of Fengdu.

34
00:02:20,319 --> 00:02:22,199
Police say they will deploy more officers

35
00:02:22,199 --> 00:02:23,120
to solve the case as soon as possible.

36
00:03:07,319 --> 00:03:07,919
Shh.

37
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:08,599
Oh.

38
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:11,280
So adorable.

39
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,560
Pigeons really love eating corn.

40
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:13,439
Really?

41
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,439
Feed them more.

42
00:03:23,199 --> 00:03:24,919
Captain Li, we found Lin Xiaohu.

43
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:32,639
Thanks for your hard work.

44
00:03:32,639 --> 00:03:33,319
Take good care of Ruolan.

45
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:33,879
Okay.

46
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:34,639
Remember,

47
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:36,719
after eight, do not let anyone in her room.

48
00:03:36,719 --> 00:03:37,400
Alright, alright.

49
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,319
Hey, Shifu.

50
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,639
I got the info on that license plate you asked for.

51
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:54,719
Good.

52
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,080
Head back to the station first.

53
00:03:56,759 --> 00:03:57,960
Then come with me to arrest Lin Xiaohu.

54
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,319
Yes, sir.

55
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,839
Jiang Han, get your clothes a bit dirty.

56
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,800
What fishmonger wears such clean clothes?

57
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:40,120
Suspected target spotted.

58
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:56,560
Copy that.

59
00:05:05,399 --> 00:05:06,800
Lin Xue, confirm the target.

60
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:08,120
Understood.

61
00:05:22,879 --> 00:05:23,720
Target confirmed.

62
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:28,680
Freeze!

63
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,879
Lin Xiaohu, freeze!

64
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,120
Freeze!

65
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,240
Freeze!

66
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:39,720
Split up!

67
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:40,600
This way!

68
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,319
Keep chasing me...

69
00:05:55,879 --> 00:05:57,360
Keep chasing me and I'll kill you!

70
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,600
Hey, Shifu, Shifu!

71
00:06:14,399 --> 00:06:15,040
Behave!

72
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,519
What did I do?

73
00:06:18,959 --> 00:06:19,600
Captain Zhao.

74
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,079
Captain Zhao.

75
00:06:35,079 --> 00:06:36,279
Director Su, you're here.

76
00:06:38,199 --> 00:06:39,879
Open up. Don't you recognize me?

77
00:06:41,079 --> 00:06:42,839
Director Su, President Xu gave orders.

78
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:44,360
Starting today, without an appointment...

79
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:46,199
...no visitors are allowed. Our hands are tied.

80
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,839
Are you kidding me?

81
00:06:49,199 --> 00:06:50,519
I need an appointment to see President Xu?

82
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:53,600
Director Su, please don't hold it against us.

83
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:55,240
Don't make things difficult for us workers.

84
00:06:58,399 --> 00:06:59,759
Director Su, please step aside.

85
00:06:59,879 --> 00:07:00,680
A car is coming.

86
00:07:10,399 --> 00:07:11,920
Director Su, why aren't you going in?

87
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:14,720
Mengmeng.

88
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,720
You've trained your subordinates well.

89
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:18,639
They don't even recognize their own.

90
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,519
Are you blind?

91
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,959
You dare block Director Su's car?

92
00:07:24,439 --> 00:07:26,000
Sister Meng, it's President Xu, she...

93
00:07:26,439 --> 00:07:27,199
Open the gate.

94
00:07:31,759 --> 00:07:32,600
After you, Brother Su.

95
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,279
Captain Li gave orders.

96
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:44,439
After eight o'clock at night,

97
00:07:44,439 --> 00:07:45,839
no one is allowed in Ruolan's room.

98
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:46,720
I'm sorry.

99
00:07:47,839 --> 00:07:48,680
Hey, Sister Ling.

100
00:07:49,079 --> 00:07:49,879
Hey, Sister Ling.

101
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:52,040
Brother Mingliang isn't an outsider.

102
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:53,519
Let him in first.

103
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,160
Ruolan.

104
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,920
The stars are beautiful tonight.

105
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,199
Let's go see the stars.

106
00:08:09,959 --> 00:08:10,439
Mm.

107
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,079
The night sky is so beautiful tonight.

108
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,079
Look.

109
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:32,159
That star is so bright!

110
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:35,000
It's winking at us.

111
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,080
Brother Su.

112
00:09:38,519 --> 00:09:39,320
Mengmeng.

113
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:42,159
You look so beautiful today.

114
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,519
Then why are you in such a hurry to leave?

115
00:09:46,159 --> 00:09:47,080
Aren't you...

116
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:48,519
going to properly...

117
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:49,960
spend some time with me?

118
00:09:52,519 --> 00:09:54,840
Oh, I'd love to.

119
00:09:55,159 --> 00:09:57,360
But I've run into some trouble lately.

120
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:03,679
What's going on with President Xu?

121
00:10:03,799 --> 00:10:05,240
She isn't answering my calls.

122
00:10:05,759 --> 00:10:06,399
Ah.

123
00:10:06,799 --> 00:10:07,840
Lately,

124
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:10,320
the group has been dealing with a lot of issues.

125
00:10:10,879 --> 00:10:12,360
To avoid being distracted,

126
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:15,240
President Xu has put her phone on Do Not Disturb.

127
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,120
I see.

128
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:19,559
Listen,

129
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,360
when you see her,

130
00:10:21,919 --> 00:10:23,159
tell her right away

131
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:25,240
that I urgently need to reach her, okay?

132
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:25,919
Okay.

133
00:10:27,519 --> 00:10:28,600
Once this is over,

134
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,759
I'll take you out, just the two of us.

135
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:40,679
Hey.

136
00:10:42,039 --> 00:10:43,000
You're already here.

137
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,600
Aren't you going to

138
00:10:45,039 --> 00:10:46,919
try the dishes I prepared for you?

139
00:10:48,399 --> 00:10:50,600
They are all fresh.

140
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:21,159
How are they? Do you like them?

141
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:22,840
Hey.

142
00:11:24,159 --> 00:11:25,440
Who's the one on the right?

143
00:11:27,559 --> 00:11:29,480
You've got quite the sharp eye.

144
00:11:29,879 --> 00:11:30,960
Her name is Xiaohong.

145
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:33,200
I just poached her from another club.

146
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:17,240
Come in.

147
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,200
Boss.

148
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:24,519
Director Su's behavior today

149
00:12:24,919 --> 00:12:25,879
was quite strange.

150
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:28,799
That man...

151
00:12:28,799 --> 00:12:30,639
He is lecherous, and even greedier.

152
00:12:30,919 --> 00:12:33,720
His days as director are likely numbered.

153
00:12:34,519 --> 00:12:36,879
So what you mean is...

154
00:12:38,399 --> 00:12:39,480
From now on, when he comes,

155
00:12:39,759 --> 00:12:41,320
just treat him as a VIP guest.

156
00:12:42,159 --> 00:12:44,240
Our group runs a legitimate business.

157
00:12:44,519 --> 00:12:46,879
We must gradually cut ties with him.

158
00:12:47,399 --> 00:12:48,440
Don't worry, boss.

159
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:01,320
Name.

160
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:08,159
Perfect timing. The interrogation just started.

161
00:13:09,279 --> 00:13:11,440
I just got back and heard you caught the suspect.

162
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:12,399
That was fast.

163
00:13:14,519 --> 00:13:15,320
I've seen you before.

164
00:13:15,879 --> 00:13:17,360
Just answer the questions.

165
00:13:17,639 --> 00:13:18,440
Name.

166
00:13:18,679 --> 00:13:19,559
I remember now.

167
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:21,320
I've given you a ride.

168
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:22,679
You've been in my car.

169
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:25,240
Lin Xiaohu.

170
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:26,960
I suggest you behave yourself.

171
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:29,759
You know I'm Xiaohu,

172
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,440
then you must also know

173
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:34,159
I didn't do anything.

174
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:35,279
Let me go.

175
00:13:35,399 --> 00:13:37,360
You know very well what you did.

176
00:13:38,279 --> 00:13:39,840
What were you doing on the night of the 23rd?

177
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:43,639
It's not the 23rd yet.

178
00:13:43,919 --> 00:13:45,559
I meant the 23rd of last month.

179
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,679
This month...

180
00:13:49,519 --> 00:13:51,320
I can't even remember what happened yesterday,

181
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:52,240
let alone last month.

182
00:13:52,559 --> 00:13:55,039
Lin Xiaohu, this is the Major Crimes Unit.

183
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:57,559
Your tantrums and tricks won't work here.

184
00:13:57,679 --> 00:13:58,480
Officer.

185
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,080
I know.

186
00:14:00,879 --> 00:14:02,240
This isn't my first time here.

187
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:04,440
If you know, then talk.

188
00:14:05,679 --> 00:14:07,120
What am I supposed to confess to, officer?

189
00:14:09,559 --> 00:14:12,000
I mean, you guys beat me up.

190
00:14:12,679 --> 00:14:14,039
My heart still hurts.

191
00:14:14,159 --> 00:14:15,039
Did you hit him?

192
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:16,679
The suspect resisted arrest with a knife.

193
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,519
I subdued him.

194
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:19,840
Is there a problem?

195
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:22,159
He's only a suspect.

196
00:14:22,919 --> 00:14:24,080
If we can't find evidence,

197
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:25,360
and he bites back at you,

198
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:26,600
you'll be in for it.

199
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:29,320
I know how to handle mad dogs.

200
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:31,039
And none of you stopped him either.

201
00:14:31,399 --> 00:14:32,159
Right now, I...

202
00:14:33,399 --> 00:14:34,120
I'm dying...

203
00:14:34,519 --> 00:14:35,639
I can't breathe.

204
00:14:35,639 --> 00:14:36,639
My heart hurts.

205
00:14:39,919 --> 00:14:40,919
Step outside for now.

206
00:14:40,919 --> 00:14:41,879
I'll go deal with him.

207
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:45,639
I'm dying...

208
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:48,080
Captain Wang.

209
00:14:53,919 --> 00:14:56,320
I am Wang Yonglin, Captain of the Major Crimes Unit.

210
00:14:57,679 --> 00:14:59,879
Oh, a boss is here.

211
00:15:00,039 --> 00:15:01,279
You came at just the right time.

212
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:04,200
That officer of yours hit me.

213
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,159
Sir, you tell me,

214
00:15:06,159 --> 00:15:08,039
which department should I complain to?

215
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:09,840
You resisted arrest with a knife,

216
00:15:10,039 --> 00:15:10,759
and assaulted a police officer.

217
00:15:11,519 --> 00:15:13,600
By law, we could have shot you on the spot.

218
00:15:13,799 --> 00:15:15,039
Shoot... shoot me?

219
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:18,919
Sir.

220
00:15:19,559 --> 00:15:21,440
I was acting in self-defense.

221
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,639
How was I supposed to know they were cops?

222
00:15:23,639 --> 00:15:25,320
I thought I was being robbed.

223
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:27,840
If you want to clear your name,

224
00:15:28,039 --> 00:15:29,879
your only way out is to cooperate with us

225
00:15:29,879 --> 00:15:31,120
and explain everything clearly.

226
00:15:31,759 --> 00:15:33,879
We would never wrong an innocent person.

227
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:41,519
Fine.

228
00:15:42,879 --> 00:15:44,360
Since the boss has spoken,

229
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:46,799
and I want to go home early too,

230
00:15:47,679 --> 00:15:48,559
So I'll talk.

231
00:15:49,279 --> 00:15:51,559
Where were you on the night of the 23rd?

232
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:54,840
On the night of the 23rd, I drove fares until 8:30.

233
00:15:55,720 --> 00:15:57,120
Then I went out drinking.

234
00:15:57,879 --> 00:16:00,399
After that, I went straight to get a massage.

235
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,080
And I got massaged until...

236
00:16:02,440 --> 00:16:03,559
Oh, I fell asleep halfway through.

237
00:16:04,279 --> 00:16:05,240
Until 12:30.

238
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:08,159
That girl woke me up.

239
00:16:08,879 --> 00:16:10,279
By the time I got home,

240
00:16:10,279 --> 00:16:11,279
it was around 1:00 a.m.

241
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:12,840
You remember it quite clearly.

242
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:15,200
Officer,

243
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:17,559
if I said I didn't remember,

244
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:18,960
you wouldn't believe me.

245
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:20,399
Now I'm telling you clearly,

246
00:16:20,799 --> 00:16:22,080
and you're unhappy again.

247
00:16:22,919 --> 00:16:25,840
Who can prove all this?

248
00:16:26,399 --> 00:16:27,799
Isn't that your job?

249
00:16:28,159 --> 00:16:29,559
You officers should go check.

250
00:16:29,799 --> 00:16:31,039
Of course we'll check.

251
00:16:33,799 --> 00:16:35,120
Do you know Shen Qing?

252
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:38,480
Who is Shen Qing?

253
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:39,679
I don't know him.

254
00:16:40,039 --> 00:16:41,879
We wouldn't have brought you in without evidence.

255
00:16:46,840 --> 00:16:47,639
My...

256
00:16:49,080 --> 00:16:50,759
in the right pocket of my jacket,

257
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:52,600
there's a receipt from that night.

258
00:17:03,679 --> 00:17:04,279
Captain Wang,

259
00:17:05,039 --> 00:17:06,200
the checkout time is

260
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:08,200
12:39 a.m. on the night of the 23rd.

261
00:17:08,480 --> 00:17:09,319
The time checks out.
